09:21.955 --> 09:25.918
Oh, I know what you mean, baby.

09:26.085 --> 09:27.503
But you just try.

09:28.212 --> 09:31.090
Let's decide that later,
after eight months at sea

09:31.256 --> 09:36.011
all I wanna do is just look at you
for a long, long time.

09:42.810 --> 09:45.938
Oh, you'll like. For sure.

09:50.985 --> 09:53.445
- Come on, get a move on.
- Come on.

09:54.905 --> 09:58.742
Come on, eight months
is a long enough time to wait.

10:01.662 --> 10:03.330
Hello?

10:04.331 --> 10:07.084
Hello, you beautiful creature.

10:07.251 --> 10:12.381
When you hear the tone, the time
will be exactly 6:10 and one quarter.

10:12.548 --> 10:14.258
Buy war bonds.

10:15.801 --> 10:18.345
Thank you, I will.

10:18.721 --> 10:21.432
Hey, you guys,
the buses for Hollywood pulled up!

10:21.598 --> 10:24.852
- Get me to Hollywood.
- Here we come.

