Goodbye. Thanks, fellas.

19:51.418 --> 19:53.837
Brooklyn, I'm blowing,
the baby's all yours.

19:54.004 --> 19:56.090
Joe. Hey, Joe!

19:56.298 --> 19:58.801
You can't leave me here,
what about my being a wolf?

19:58.968 --> 20:02.054
