What will become of me?

20:10.938 --> 20:13.732
Okay. Okay.

20:21.115 --> 20:23.367
Who's he calling?

20:23.534 --> 20:25.452
A girl.

20:26.829 --> 20:29.498
Lola, baby.

20:30.290 --> 20:31.834
Forgotten you?

20:32.001 --> 20:33.919
Oh, honey.

20:34.086 --> 20:37.006
With the picture of you
I've got in my mind?

20:37.172 --> 20:40.968
Why, even across the phone,
I can see every...

20:43.262 --> 20:45.139
Look, let me tell you what happened.

20:45.306 --> 20:49.435
- I found a kid that was lost.
- Joe, I wasn't lost.

20:52.229 --> 20:55.691
So I had to take him home.
I won't be long.

20:57.776 --> 21:03.532
As long as I get there?
Oh, honey, you know I'll get there.

21:07.036 --> 21:09.955
Look, we better talk
about that later, huh?

21:10.164 --> 21:13.792
- Yeah, goodbye.
- What are you going to talk about later?

21:15.377 --> 21:17.087
Things, sailor. Things.

21:17.254 --> 21:19.006
You'll understand when you get older.

21:19.173 --> 21:24.470
- Everybody keeps saying that to me.
- Yeah, they used to say that to me too.

21:24.637 --> 21:27.556
Well, did you understand
when you got older?

21:27.681 --> 21:29.391
Nope.

21:29.933 --> 21:32.269
I wonder what could be keeping
that Aunt Susie.

21:32.436 --> 21:34.688
What can an old lady
be doing out this late?

21:51.330 --> 21:53.999
Susan, don't you wish
that you were up there?

21:54.166 --> 21:58.087
